would love an update.

34
00:03:26.623 --> 00:03:27.874
{\an8}- Poison.
- Poison.

35
00:03:27.958 --> 00:03:29.459
{\an8}- How do you know?
- Lips are blue.

36
00:03:29.543 --> 00:03:32.421
{\an8}EMT said they were blue
